title: How Do Surprise Contenders Fit in to the Title-Race Hierarchy? | Group Chat
description:
Justin, Rob, and Wos discuss whether the Warriors (2:36), Heat (18:38), Wizards (31:31), and Bulls (40:44) are championship contenders.

Producer: Brian H. Waters
